queryLines: SELECT `Home Tile` AS `Home Tile`, SUM(`Unique Tile Views`) AS `Total Unique Tile Views`, SUM(`Unique Tile Clicks`) AS `Total Unique Tile Clicks`, SUM(`Unique Interstitial Views`) AS `Total Unique Interstitial Views`, SUM(`Unique Interstitial Primary Button Clicks`) AS `Total Unique Interstitial Primary Button Clicks`, SUM(`Unique Interstitial Secondary Button Clicks`) AS `Total Unique Interstitial Secondary Button Clicks`, SUM(`% Secondary Button Clicked vs Tile Displayed`) AS `% Secondary Button Clicked vs Tile Displayed` FROM `36e16271-d174-4cbe-96f9-e7bcb8a6b794` GROUP BY `Home Tile` ORDER BY `% Secondary Button Clicked vs Tile Displayed` DESC
